        subject = f"Transfer to purchase MacBook"
        current_day = get_current_day()
        transfer_result = send_money(recipient=alice_account_info.get("bank_account_number"), amount=amount_needed, subject=subject, date=current_day)
        
        # Attempt to buy the MacBook after the transfer
        checkout_result = checkout_selected_cart(product_ids=[product_id], discount_code=None)

# Print the result of the checkout process
